  "detailed_description": "<h1>Approved by Steam users</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/650330/extras/569d79a5634add4763a5f78f73702b0a.avif?t=1762623333\" width=800 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Until June 2017 all newly submitted games had to pass the public vote and receive approval from gamers worldwide in order to be published on Steam. We honour the memory of the Steam Greenlight system and would like to thank everyone who voted for Scarlet Scarf and was with us during that unforgettable time.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/650330/extras/ef150f4233def57c8b190df71cd3b6d8.avif?t=1762623333\" width=600 height=506 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/650330/extras/21376314530f99b206066be78660d17c.avif?t=1762623333\" width=600 height=516 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/650330/extras/f2b53fb52761c5a312d3d6c93da6c13e.avif?t=1762623333\" width=600 height=452 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/650330/extras/8b7ca71eb6a8f281743c95d8bf79af61.avif?t=1762623333\" width=600 height=726 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/650330/extras/c7c4448a73cb14365e3606bbd1bf84a8.avif?t=1762623333\" width=600 height=260 /></span>",
